    {
      "text": "<b>Therefore</b>, when creating the plan, keep these unforeseen requirements in mind by including time buffers. Because unforeseen topics will come up in any seminar, it is safe to incorporate these time buffers from the beginning. If not, you can finish early! However, be sure not to drift too far from your <i>[[SEMINAR PLAN]]</i>. If a question is completely out of the scope of the seminar, answer it off-line.\n  ",
      "id": "8b40490fce719945",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
