      "text": "The schedule can contain periods marked as buffers, or, alternatively, some parts of the content could be marked as \"optional\", these parts can then be replaced by one of the unplanned topics. If the unplanned topic is similar to a planned example consider replacing the example with the unplanned topic.\n  ",
